edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage

Class Garage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage.Garage

  • public class Garage
extends java.lang.Object
    Class serves as a list archetype to hold ServiceBay objects and manage their number. Garage starts with 8 open ServiceBays and can open a maximum of 30 total bays. Every third bay opened is automatically opened as a HybridElectricBay.
    Author:
    Nick Garner
